text: LA-19 is a constituency of Azad Kashmir Legislative Assembly which is currently represented by the Sardar Khalid Ibrahim Khan of Jammu Kashmir Peoples Party. It covers the area of Rawalakot in Poonch District of Azad Kashmir, Pakistan. ==Election 2016== elections were held in this constituency on 21 July 2016. ==References== Category:Government of Azad Kashmir Category:Constituencies of Pakistan Category:Poonch District, Pakistan
title: Constituency LA-19
